{"tid":1867121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幾百蚊盒/排通宵既口罩要買既同我入晒黎！","createTime":"2020-02-07T05:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T05:04:58.000Z","uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"694d036bed1262f99d8ade939f133edf2c693747","tid":1867121,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:01:03.000Z","msg":"我明白大家都好想保護好自己或者屋企人<br />\n但有無諗過一個口罩根本唔能夠完全防禦<br />\n如果你係咁驚死 <br />\n你帶左防護眼罩未 帶左手套未？<br />\n好多人根本淨係帶個口罩 就當自己做左野<br />\n你隻手污糟既程度<br />\n根本大過你比人噴口水既機會<br />\n不過手套唔帶 只愛口罩？<br />\n無口罩既 為左撲個口罩返黎貴一貴到買<br />\n排通宵吹成晚風都制 <br />\n明明口罩只係其中一個防禦方法<br />\n明明仲有其他方法 但唔做唔買 <br />\n淨係想搶口罩？<br />\n我真係開始懷疑啲人係enjoy搶個個過程<br />\n你地醒下啦<br />\n<br />\nBtw 兩盒thx<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MO4zm88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMO4zm88.jpg&h=d57ad522&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ad64614f8883ccefa592ac7ca6956f22c6c9452","tid":1867121,"uid":50622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:02:37.000Z","msg":"其實手套同眼罩都有人搶緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4504f72976f4eef228554bfc0685635da8ebb84","tid":1867121,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:04:01.000Z","msg":"兩盒thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdfc989a0622bf1f9aacff28f9a7a69067fe2b1","tid":1867121,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ad64614f8883ccefa592ac7ca6956f22c6c9452","tid":1867121,"uid":50622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:02:37.000Z","msg":"其實手套同眼罩都有人搶緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:04:58.000Z","msg":"係囉 搶囉<br />\n你自己望下條街有幾成人帶梗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}